WHO   — Murbella — the bridge between two matriarchies
WHAT  — An Honored Matre captured by the Bene Gesserit who, against all expectation, takes the Sisterhood's training.
WHERE — D1 · Dune  Framework inputs: Chapterhouse — the Bene Gesserit and the Honored Matres  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
